# Overview

We are looking for a Back-end Team Lead to drive the development and scalability of our digital product Yourshot http://yourshot.nationalgeographic.com/
Product has been live for 5 years, this person will work closely with the product owner to determine development needs for feature adds such as, follow/friends, redo-onboarding and redesign.

Candidates for this role should be fully proficient in Python, Django and some front-end technologies. Having experience or an interest in new technologies-node.js, Go, etc is a plus! Must have consumer facing product devlopment expereince or enterprise/internal apps development exp with at least 30k users, scability is vital for this project.


Please send a CV to the address above.

# Role requirements

* Python
* Django
* PostgreSQL
* Javascript
* Puppet
